## 3. Prohibited Uses

Without prior written permission from the appropriate rights holder, you may not:

### 3.1 Source code and implementation

* Copy the source code.
* Fork the repository for reuse.
* Reuse the code in another project.
* Modify the code to create a derivative website or product.
* Redistribute the source code.
* Publish the source code elsewhere.
* Sell, rent, sublicense, or commercially exploit the code.
* Use the code as a template, starter, boilerplate, or tutorial project.
* Deploy a copy of this website to another domain, platform, or hosting provider.
* Convert the code into another framework or technology stack for reuse.
* Use any portion of the calculator logic, pricing implementation, layout, components, or project structure in another project.

### 3.2 Design and user interface

* Copy the website design.
* Recreate the visual layout for another project.
* Use the color system, component arrangement, page structure, or interaction patterns as a directly copied template.
* Create a confusingly similar website, brand presentation, or commission calculator based on this project.

### 3.3 Artwork, images, and content

* Download, copy, repost, redistribute, or re-upload artwork or portfolio images.
* Use artwork in another website, product, social media post, dataset, model, merchandise, or commercial project.
* Modify, crop, trace, recolor, edit, remix, or create derivative works from artwork without permission.
* Remove or obscure watermarks, signatures, notices, or attribution.
* Use Gosofia's artwork, name, brand, logo, or portfolio content to imply endorsement or affiliation.

### 3.4 AI, dataset, machine learning, and automated extraction

* Use any source code, text, artwork, images, or project content from this repository for AI training, machine learning datasets, model fine-tuning, dataset creation, prompt datasets, evaluation datasets, synthetic data generation, or automated model ingestion.
* Scrape, crawl, bulk download, mirror, index, or extract this repository or website content for dataset or machine-learning purposes.
* Use the artwork, text, calculator logic, or website content as input data for generative AI systems, image-generation models, code-generation models, or automated derivative-work systems.

### 3.5 NFT, tokenization, and blockchain use

* Mint, tokenize, sell, list, register, or otherwise use any code, artwork, image, brand asset, or project content as or in connection with NFTs, blockchain tokens, digital collectibles, or similar systems.

### 3.6 Commercial and client use

* Use this repository to build a paid client project.
* Use this repository as a deliverable for another client.
* Use this repository in a commercial template, theme, SaaS product, marketplace item, or design kit.
* Use the code or design to compete with, impersonate, or replace the original Gosofia Studio website.

